  "detailed_description": "<strong>Grippy Golf</strong> is a speedrunning 3D platformer where objects stick to the ball.  Launch yourself across the course, collecting an ever-growing cluster of objects as you aim for a hole in one!<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Maintain Your Momentum</h2>Boost from one powerup to the next to finish each level in a single stroke.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2299080/extras/1338c1d6e3c5ad996a46a0629c023274.poster.avif?t=1708794120\" width=600 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2299080/extras/1338c1d6e3c5ad996a46a0629c023274.webm?t=1708794120\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2299080/extras/1338c1d6e3c5ad996a46a0629c023274.mp4?t=1708794120\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Stick to Anything</h2>Cones, trees, houses...  Increase your mass to gather bigger objects.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2299080/extras/1f2c9aa1a363dd757435e39fe32cd85e.poster.avif?t=1708794120\" width=600 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2299080/extras/1f2c9aa1a363dd757435e39fe32cd85e.webm?t=1708794120\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2299080/extras/1f2c9aa1a363dd757435e39fe32cd85e.mp4?t=1708794120\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Master the Course</h2>Test your cleverness and skill by completing bonus objectives and competing on the leaderboard.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2299080/extras/69231c0dece3bb4763ed8466703fb1a8.poster.avif?t=1708794120\" width=600 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2299080/extras/69231c0dece3bb4763ed8466703fb1a8.webm?t=1708794120\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2299080/extras/69231c0dece3bb4763ed8466703fb1a8.mp4?t=1708794120\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Unlock Strange Items</h2>Acquire new golf balls, like... a hairbrush?  A golf club??<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2299080/extras/d41f9be72ce2b67cacd8014eb981853b.poster.avif?t=1708794120\" width=600 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2299080/extras/d41f9be72ce2b67cacd8014eb981853b.webm?t=1708794120\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2299080/extras/d41f9be72ce2b67cacd8014eb981853b.mp4?t=1708794120\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
  "about_the_game": "<strong>Grippy Golf</strong> is a speedrunning 3D platformer where objects stick to the ball.  Launch yourself across the course, collecting an ever-growing cluster of objects as you aim for a hole in one!<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Maintain Your Momentum</h2>Boost from one powerup to the next to finish each level in a single stroke.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2299080/extras/1338c1d6e3c5ad996a46a0629c023274.poster.avif?t=1708794120\" width=600 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2299080/extras/1338c1d6e3c5ad996a46a0629c023274.webm?t=1708794120\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2299080/extras/1338c1d6e3c5ad996a46a0629c023274.mp4?t=1708794120\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Stick to Anything</h2>Cones, trees, houses...  Increase your mass to gather bigger objects.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2299080/extras/1f2c9aa1a363dd757435e39fe32cd85e.poster.avif?t=1708794120\" width=600 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2299080/extras/1f2c9aa1a363dd757435e39fe32cd85e.webm?t=1708794120\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2299080/extras/1f2c9aa1a363dd757435e39fe32cd85e.mp4?t=1708794120\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Master the Course</h2>Test your cleverness and skill by completing bonus objectives and competing on the leaderboard.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_